                <r3d:description language="eng">The U.S. Antarctic Program Data Center (USAP-DC) provides the central Project Catalog  for projects funded by the NSF for the U.S. Antarctic Program and  Data Repository for multi-disciplinary investigator research datasets derived from these projects. Services provided support investigators in documenting, preserving, and disseminating their research results. All data are openly accessible to the international community for browse, search, and data download. Datasets are registered in the Antarctic Master Directory to comply with the Antarctic Treaty.</r3d:description>
